ieval England, normally pronounced ‘Water’."],"variants":[{"name":"Walther","meanings":["from <i>wald</i> ‘rule’ + <i>heri</i> ‘army’; name of the famous medieval minnesinger  Walther von der Vogelweide  (  <i>c.</i>1170– <i>c.</i>1230 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Walter VON KLINGEN was born in 1095. He had at least 2 sons."},"et":{"1095–":"1095–Surnud","1119–1150":"1119–1150","1120–Male":"1120–Surnud","1095–Male":"1095–Surnud","1120":"1120","1095":"1095","1150":"1150","1119":"1119"},"fi":{"1095–":"1095–Kuollut","1119–1150":"1119–1150","1120–Male":"1120–Kuollut","1095–Male":"1095–Kuollut","1120":"1120","1095":"1095","1150":"1150","1119":"1119"},"fr":{"1095–":"1095–Décédé","1119–1150":"1119–1150","1120–Male":"1120–Décédé","1095–Male":"1095–Décédé","1120":"1120","1095":"1095","1150":"1150","1119":"1119","lifeSummary":"Walter VON KLINGEN est né en 1095. Il a eu au moins 2 fils."},"de":{"1095–":"1095–Verstorben","1119–1150":"1119–1150","1120–Male":"1120–Verstorben","1095–Male":"1095–Verstorben","1120":"1120","1095":"1095","1150":"1150","1119":"1119","lifeSummary":"Walter VON KLINGEN wurde 1095 geboren. Er hatte mindestens 2 Söhne."},"ht":{"1095–":"1095–Desede","1119–1150":"1119–1150","1120–Male":"1120–Desede","1095–Male":"1095–Desede","1120":"1120","1095":"1095","1150":"1150","1119":"1119"},"hu":{"1095–":"1095–elhunyt","1119–1150":"1119–1150","1120–Male":"1120–elhunyt","1095–Male":"1095–elhunyt","1120":"1120","1095":"1095","1150":"1150","1119":"1119"},"id":{"1095–":"1095–Telah Meninggal","1119–1150":"1119–1150","1120–Male":"1120–Telah Meninggal","1095–Male":"1095–Telah Meninggal","1120":"1120","1095":"1095","1150":"1150","1119":"1119"},"it":{"1095–":"1095–Deceduto","1119–1150":"1119–1150","1120–Male":"1120–Deceduto","1095–Male":"1095–Deceduto","1120":"1120","1095":"1095","1150":"1150","1119":"1119","lifeSummary":"Walter VON KLINGEN è nato il nel 1095. Lui avuto almeno 2 figli."},"ja":{"1095–":"1095年–死亡","1119–1150":"1119年–1150年","1120–Male":"1120年–死亡","1095–Male":"1095年–死亡",